# app-ads.txt Example File
# 
# When your AdSense account is set up, you will receive the necessary ads.txt code.
# Copy that code here and rename this file to app-ads.txt
#
# Format:
# <publisher_domain.com>, <direct_publisher_id>, <certification_authority_id>, <relationship_type>, <certification_auth_id>
#
# Example (replace with your actual data when you get it from AdSense):
# google.com, pub-XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX, DIRECT, f08c47fec0942fa0

# For more information about app-ads.txt and Google Play, visit:
# https://support.google.com/googleplay/android-developer/answer/10788723